long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SvelteScope empowers developers to ship more confident Svelte code by pinpointing unexpected behaviors and experiment with components non-destructively - all within the browser! 

The extension allows users to visualize their Svelte projects' components via an interactive component tree, and to live-edit their component props without altering the existing codebase.
